ru-acronym of/documentation:

{{documentation subpage}}
==Usage==
This template is used to properly format a Russian [[acronym]]. The word or words may or may not have direct or indirect links. If a term does not exist in Wiktionary and is not an appropriate entry, the link may go to Wikipedia. The following parameters exist:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description !! Notes
|-
| <code>1</code> || if {{para|2}} is empty, {{para|1}} is what the acronym stands for, as it is to be displayed, with the page link automatically derived from it; else, it is the page to link to, with the display form specified separately in {{para|2}} || normally required
|-
| <code>2</code> || see comments for {{para|1}} || normally omitted
|-
| <code>3</code> || English-language gloss || optional
|-
| <code>tr</code> || Manual transliteration || normally omitted, defaulting to the automatic transliteration of the display form
|-
| <code>cap</code> || If non-empty, capitalize the first letter of ''acronym'' || normally omitted
|-
| <code>dot</code> || If non-empty, punctuation to emit after the rest of the template || normally omitted, and no punctuation will be emitted
|}

The page is automatically placed in the categories [[:Category:Russian acronyms]] and [[:Category:Russian abbreviations]].

;Examples:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Word !! Kode !! Result !! Notes
|-
| {{m|ru|ВОВ}} || <code><nowiki>{{ru-acronym of|Вели́кая Оте́чественная война́||[[Great Patriotic War]]}} {{gloss|World War II}}</nowiki></code> || {{ru-acronym of|Вели́кая Оте́чественная война́||[[Great Patriotic War]]}} {{gloss|World War II}} || links to the page named ''Великая Отечественная война'' (accents automatically stripped)
|-
| {{m|ru|вуз}} || <code><nowiki>{{ru-acronym of|[[высший|вы́сшее]] [[учебный|уче́бное]] [[заведе́ние]]||higher/highest educational establishment}}: [[university]], [[college]], [[institute]]</nowiki></code> || {{ru-acronym of|[[высший|вы́сшее]] [[учебный|уче́бное]] [[заведе́ние]]||higher/highest educational establishment}}: [[university]], [[college]], [[institute]] || link to individual words (a bare link like <code><nowiki>[[заведе́ние]]</nowiki></code> is automatically accent-stripped to produce a link to the page named ''заведение''); note literal meaning using the gloss param, and fluent definition following the template
|-
| {{m|ru|ГЛОНА́СС}} || <code><nowiki>{{ru-acronym of|[[глобальный|ГЛОбальная]] [[навигация|НАвигационная]] [[спутник|Спутниковая]] [[система|Система]]}}: [[GLONASS]], Global Navigation Satellite System ([[GPS]])</nowiki></code> || {{ru-acronym of|[[глобальный|ГЛОбальная]] [[навигация|НАвигационная]] [[спутник|Спутниковая]] [[система|Система]]}}: [[GLONASS]], Global Navigation Satellite System ([[GPS]]) || note that the definition includes the corresponding English acronym for the system
|}
