;Examples:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Word !! Kode !! Result !! Notes
|-
| {{m|ru|АК-47}} || <code><nowiki>{{ru-etym initialism of|[[автома́т Кала́шникова]] 1947}}, from the name of the designer [[w:Mikhail Kalashnikov|Mikhail Kalashnikov]].</nowiki></code> || {{ru-etym initialism of|[[автома́т Кала́шникова]] 1947}}, from the name of the designer [[w:Mikhail Kalashnikov|Mikhail Kalashnikov]]. || link to individual words (a bare link like <code><nowiki>[[автома́т Кала́шникова]]</nowiki></code> is automatically accent-stripped to produce a link to the page named ''автомат Калашникова'')
